/F1 9.5 Tf
10.9249999999999989 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
48. 708. Td
(Koheez.ai is a HIPAA-regulated clinical decision support platform serving AHF pharmacy teams across multiple regions.) Tj
T* (This document provides a current-state assessment of the platform architecture, authentication model, data storage,) Tj
T* (external integrations, and security posture as of July 2026 following the completion of Task #137 \(Security Hardening —) Tj
T* (Code-Only Fixes\).) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9.5 Tf
10.9249999999999989 TL
0.059 0.09 0.165 rg
48. 644. Td
(A governance audit conducted in July 2026 identified 20 risk items across Critical, High, Medium, and Low severity bands.) Tj
T* (Of these, 13 were addressable through code changes alone. Task #137 resolved 9 of those 13 items. The remaining 4) Tj
T* (code-addressable items are tracked in follow-up tasks \(#138 and #139\). The remaining 7 items require external vendor) Tj
T* (coordination, infrastructure provisioning, or contractual agreements \(BAAs\) and are catalogued in the Remaining Risk) Tj
T* (Register.) Tj
ET
